  "name": "RPlog_The_Red_Line_Express",
  "title": "The Red Line Express",
  "summary": "In the oppressive interrogation suite of the Star Destroyer Nemesis, the captured ambassador Ambrosia Ad-Delgard -- designated prisoner 78492 -- is broken down by thirst, hunger, and sleep deprivation after days without water or medical care. Drifting through hallucinations and guarding a phantom pregnancy in her addled mind, she cowers as a bored, greasy-haired Imperial agent and two stormtroopers haul her to her feet for another session. Slowly clawing her way back to lucidity, Ambrosia accuses the agent of having spilled her water and, under questioning, confirms her occupation as the rebel Alliance's ambassador to Caspar and recounts how she first came to the post after Dean Corso's assassination and was sent back the second time by Captain Cen. As she names names and chases imaginary orbs of light, her dehydrated body finally red-lines: she collapses, gagging and gasping, and the agent calmly suspends the interrogation, calling a medical response for severe dehydration and potential respiratory arrest.",
